# Analytics credentials
# Umami API key: ~/.config/audiocontrol/umami-key.json
# Umami website ID is hardcoded (2b9a4087-e93a-432d-adba-252233404d67)

# Feature image generation
# Preferred: keep keys in ~/.config/audiocontrol/ — the CLI auto-loads them at runtime.
#   openai-key.txt → OPENAI_API_KEY (DALL-E 3)
#   flux-key.txt   → BFL_API_KEY    (FLUX 1.1 Pro via Black Forest Labs)
# Environment variables override the file-based keys when set:
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# BFL_API_KEY=
